The MPC system is installed in LT as an additional control system. The MPC system also adopts optimization formulation as described in Eq. (2). The MPC system minimizes the cooling power provided by the chilled water (Qcw
                        ) supplied into the AHU and indoor PMV index. Qcw
                         is calculated using flowrate, supply temperature and return temperature of the chilled water as shown in Eq. (9).
